import React from 'react';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Button } from '@mui/material';

const Navbar = ({ logout, token }) => {
    return (
        <header>
            <nav className='Navbar'>
                <Button>
                    <Link
                        style=
                        {{ textDecoration: 'none' }}
                        to='/'>
                        Home
                    </Link>
                </Button>
                <Button>
                    <Link
                        style=
                        {{ textDecoration: 'none' }}
                        to='/posts'>
                        Posts
                    </Link>
                </Button>
                {
                    token ? (
                        <>
                            <Button>
                                <Link
                                    style=
                                    {{ textDecoration: 'none' }}
                                    to='/profile'>
                                    Profile
                                </Link>
                            </Button>
                            <Button>
                                <Link
                                    style=
                                    {{ textDecoration: 'none' }}
                                    to='/'
                                    onClick={() => logout()}>
                                    Logout
                                </Link>
                            </Button>
                        </>
                    ) : (
                        <Button>
                            <Link
                                style=
                                {{ textDecoration: 'none' }}
                                to='/login'>
                                Login
                            </Link>
                        </Button>
                    )
                }
            </nav>
        </header>
    )
}

export default Navbar;
